text: “mi mi sing dı khadkhwang phwk khea nı kar thi brrda sing bricakh khxng phwk khea mi thuk rab cak phwk khea nxkcak phwk khea ptiseth sraththa tx xallxh læa tx rx sul khxng phraxngkh theanan læa phwk khea ca mi ma lahmad nxkcak phwk khea ca mi sphaph keiyckhran læ phwk khea ca mi bricakh nxkcak phwk khea ca mi sphaph fun cı”
